00:51:11.548 --> 00:51:14.449
Yeah. yeah aunt sure
hundred percent.

773
00:51:14.918 --> 00:51:18.354
Aunt. Ayesha?
- She is in her room.

774
00:51:18.822 --> 00:51:19.880
