Wait. wait you asked Simi for
what Shantu said to you.

796
00:52:54.818 --> 00:52:58.481
l didnt ask her. we were just
talking and.. - No. no. no.

797
00:52:58.956 --> 00:53:03.518
That means you are still verifying
you dont trust me.

798
00:53:03.660 --> 00:53:06.561
No. its not like that Simi was
just teasing me about you..

799
