Oh very good. even Simi
is making fun of me now.

800
00:53:13.504 --> 00:53:15.734
Rohan. whats wrong with
you its just girl talk.

801
00:53:15.806 --> 00:53:18.331
You dont know anything. stay
away from that Simi..

802
00:53:18.408 --> 00:53:20.467
..she is smarter than she looks.

803
00:53:20.744 --> 00:53:23.577
Rohan. now what problem
do you have with Simi.

804
00:53:23.947 --> 00:53:25.437
