will l talk to..

808
00:53:32.422 --> 00:53:34.549
..and whom will l not talk to?

809
00:53:34.725 --> 00:53:36.420
First Shantu and now Simi.

810
00:53:36.493 --> 00:53:40.827
Shantu. so you miss
talking to Shantu.

811
00:53:42.633 --> 00:53:44.362
Rohan. l was just giving an example..

812
00:53:44.434 --> 00:53:47.426
