wrong meaning of everything.

813
00:53:47.504 --> 00:53:51.497
l am wrong. and Shantu is
right. then go to him.

814
00:53:53.810 --> 00:53:55.835
Rohan. why are you
acting so immature.

815
00:53:56.013 --> 00:53:57.605
