827
00:55:03.113 --> 00:55:05.877
Hello. Ayesha. hi dear.

828
00:55:05.983 --> 00:55:08.543
Mom please. l dont
want to talk to her.

829
00:55:08.685 --> 00:55:11.051
What happened aunt. he has still
not returned? - Rohan is..

830
00:55:11.121 --> 00:55:12.554
Please. l dont want to talk to her.

831
00:55:12.656 --> 00:55:14.453
Tell her that l have gone
to the club with Vasu.

832
00:55:14.524 --> 00:55:16.116
Just tell her l dont
want to talk to her.

833
00:55:16.526 --> 00:55:18.460
Tell her that l am in the club.
l dont want to talk to her.

834
00:55:18.528 --> 00:55:19.859
You had called to say bye.

835
00:55:20.964 --> 00:55:22.989
Yes dear. l will ask
him to call you up.

836
00:55:23.533 --> 00:55:25.933
Thanks aunt.
- Bye. take care.

837
00:55:26.003 --> 00:55:27.061
Bye.

838
00:55:30.107 --> 00:55:33.634
To say bye. why where am l going?

839
00:55:33.844 --> 00:55:36.472
Not you she is going to Paris
along with her mom..

840
00:55:36.546 --> 00:55:38.605
..by tomorrow morning flight.

841
00:55:39.116 --> 00:55:41.914
What is happening Rohan. this
was her 3rd call. - Oh fish..

842
00:55:42.019 --> 00:55:44.647
Dont you have any
courtesy to say bye?

843
00:55:46.223 --> 00:55:49.590
And clean that mess right now.
