844
00:55:58.568 --> 00:56:01.093
Ayesha. l have kept the
heels in your bags.

845
00:56:02.039 --> 00:56:03.097
What happened?

846
00:56:04.908 --> 00:56:06.000
Dear.

847
00:56:07.210 --> 00:56:08.609
Dont worry dear.

848
00:56:09.613 --> 00:56:13.777
Dear. he will surely come to
