Now both the dogs were
tied to the same bench.

922
01:02:38.268 --> 01:02:40.395
The lease was of the
same colour too.

923
01:02:41.504 --> 01:02:44.302
Maybe by mistake..
- By mistake l married you!

924
01:02:46.109 --> 01:02:48.168
One day mistakenly you
will change your wife.

925
01:02:50.380 --> 01:02:51.438
Mistakenly..

926
01:03:14.104 --> 01:03:19.132
You have gone. l am still here.

927
01:03:19.542 --> 01:03:22.602
Still l am not here.

928
01:03:22.679 --> 01:03:27.013
Do you know when you are not there.

929
01:03:28.017 --> 01:03:31.544
Nothing seems to be right.

930
01:03:31.621 --> 01:03:39.153
Everything thats happening l
cannot understand anything.

931
01:03:39.329 --> 01:03:43.129
My heart is where you are

932
01:03:43.366 --> 01:03:48.030
l cannot tolerate this distance.

933
01:03:48.104 --> 01:03:53.064
You have gone. l am still here.

934
01:03:53.209 --> 01:03:56.372
Still l am not here.

935
01:03:56.446 --> 01:04:01.577
Do you know when
you are not there?

936
01:04:01.651 --> 01:04:06.213
Nothing seems to be right.

937
01:04:06.523 --> 01:04:13.691
Yes. this is what you call love.

938
01:04:14.731 --> 01:04:23.435
Yes. this is what you call love.

939
01:04:41.591 --> 01:04:44.219
Yes l win. come on give me ten.

940
01:04:45.128 --> 01:04:46.288
What has happened to you?

941
01:04:48.231 --> 01:04:51.029
Sudheer. shall
l tell you something..

942
01:04:51.100 --> 01:04:54.297
..will you laugh.
- No. tell me.

943
01:04:59.742 --> 01:05:03.041
l.. first you promise me
that you wont laugh..

944
01:05:03.112 --> 01:05:06.206
..and you wont tell anyone.

945
01:05:06.649 --> 01:05:12.110
And you wont tease you.
- Okay. l wont now tell me.

946
01:05:12.589 --> 01:05:13.647
Okay.

947
01:05:16.226 --> 01:05:18.751
l..
- Tell me.

948
01:05:19.662 --> 01:05:24.565
That.. - lts time for me to
go home. l am going home

949
01:05:24.634 --> 01:05:26.261
l am missing Ayesha.

950
01:05:37.347 --> 01:05:39.440
Missing Ayesha.

951
01:06:03.773 --> 01:06:06.241
Hello. hello.

952
01:06:08.478 --> 01:06:09.604
Hello.

953
01:06:12.615 --> 01:06:14.207
Hi.
- Oh. hi.

954
01:06:14.350 --> 01:06:16.113
Where to? - Painting classes.
its a new project..

955
01:06:16.185 --> 01:06:18.415
