Then do one thing. go to Paris.

970
01:07:12.241 --> 01:07:13.333
What else?

971
01:07:13.543 --> 01:07:16.603
Go to the Eiffel Tower and
tell her everything.

972
01:07:17.246 --> 01:07:18.543
