976
01:07:25.321 --> 01:07:29.280
You take everything
seriously. Devdas.

977
01:07:30.426 --> 01:07:31.654
My ten rupees.

978
01:07:32.261 --> 01:07:33.421
l am very late today.

979
01:07:35.264 --> 01:07:36.322
Hello.

980
01:07:36.799 --> 01:07:37.857
Yes. just a second.

981
