- Bye. - Bye.

982
01:07:40.636 --> 01:07:43.366
Hello.
- Hey Ayesha.

983
01:07:43.573 --> 01:07:44.631
Hey what a surprise.

984
01:07:44.741 --> 01:07:48.700
