985
01:07:48.778 --> 01:07:51.747
Hi Ruhi. you were in New York.

986
01:07:51.814 --> 01:07:54.544
Now l am here. l wanted
to meet the friends..

987
01:07:54.617 --> 01:07:55.777
Tell her to come here.
