993
01:08:10.566 --> 01:08:12.932
Yeah. but..
- Hey. dont be a fool.

994
01:08:13.302 --> 01:08:17.739
You can come to France
but not London.

995
01:08:17.807 --> 01:08:19.331
You have to come.

996
01:08:19.542 --> 01:08:20.907
lts just two hours away.
we will have a blast.

997
01:08:20.977 --> 01:08:23.775
Come on. this weekend
we will see you here.

998
01:08:23.846 --> 01:08:25.404
Whos that. is that Ayesha?

999
01:08:25.615 --> 01:08:27.742
And talk to Doris when you
come here. okay bye.

1000
01:08:27.817 --> 01:08:28.875
Love you. see you.

1001
01:08:37.960 --> 01:08:41.657
My dad proposed to my mom here.
near the Eiffel Tower.

1002
01:08:42.331 --> 01:08:43.855
Thats the most romantic
thing to do.

1003
01:08:43.966 --> 01:08:46.264
Not you she is leaving. along
with her mom to Paris..

1004
01:08:46.335 --> 01:08:48.394
..with the morning flight.

1005
01:08:48.538 --> 01:08:50.631
Then do one thing. go to Paris.

1006
01:08:50.706 --> 01:08:52.970
Do you know. why l feel that
the Eiffel is so romantic?

1007
01:08:53.443 --> 01:08:57.777
20 years ago my dad proposed
to my mom here.

1008
01:08:59.816 --> 01:09:02.842
And then their first kiss.

1009
01:09:18.367 --> 01:09:20.392
Call the doctor. he has gone mad.

1010
01:09:20.536 --> 01:09:23.300
lt is a nonsense idea.
Paris is not near Mussoorie..

1011
01:09:23.372 --> 01:09:25.306
..that you left in the morning.
toured the place..

1012
01:09:25.374 --> 01:09:27.899
..and return in the evening.

1013
01:09:28.711 --> 01:09:30.804
Where is the lemonade?
- There.

1014
01:09:30.880 --> 01:09:31.938
Give me.

1015
01:09:32.381 --> 01:09:34.474
Sorry guys. actually Farhas
had called and..

1016
01:09:35.485 --> 01:09:38.010
