1433
01:40:47.488 --> 01:40:50.355
Sameer.. - Go quickly. l can
stop them for only an hour.

1434
01:40:50.424 --> 01:40:51.482
You must leave.. go..

1435
01:40:51.925 --> 01:40:54.894
You must be thinking that..

1436
01:40:55.896 --> 01:40:56.954
lf you try to understand girls..

1437
01:40:57.031 --> 01:40:58.760
..then you will have to dedicate
your entire life.

1438
